snippet.title: Post Industrial New Revolution
snippet.description:
Post ndustrial new revolution from the last days of human kind as we know on this planet call it earth.

The place for all kind of bands or albums mainly of industrial rock but also rouding in the genere of Industrial music, classic bands, not classic bands and some new bands or undergrounds bands.

Thanks to all these artists for make this great music and make life more exciting. I enjoy.

You enjoy it

X

(I do NOT make any money with the videos of this channel, all the money from the ads of the videos goes directly to the bands / publishers / record company, I only upload these bands to enjoy  their music and to make known the industrial music/scene in a channel.)

Now I got a paypal account, If you want now you can donate, for upload more albums and if all going well and growing I will make another channel with news, other stuff and underground bands. Greetings to all!!!
https://paypal.me/postindustrialnewrev

For underground bands album submission go to Patreon link.
.
